ck is the brand of the youth. One of Titan\'s own products, <b><a style=\\\"color: #1a75ff;\\\" title=\\\"Fastrack watches\\\" href=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.titan.co.in\\/shop\\/watches\\/brand=fastrack\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\" rel=\\\"noopener\\\">Fastrack watches<\\/a><\\/b>, aims to complement millennial\'s active lifestyle and trends. From smartwatches to <b><a style=\\\"color: #1a75ff;\\\" title=\\\"analog watches\\\" href=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.titan.co.in\\/shop\\/analog-watches\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\" rel=\\\"noopener\\\"> analog watches<\\/a><\\/b>, you can find a variety of styles and designs online on our website.<\\/p><h3>\\u2022 Sonata<\\/h3><p>A bold and contemporary product of TATA, to <b><a style=\\\"color: #1a75ff;\\\" title=\\\"Sonata watches\\\" href=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.titan.co.in\\/shop\\/sonata-watches\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\" rel=\\\"noopener\\\"> Sonata watches<\\/a><\\/b> accentuate every outfit with their classic designs. Affordable and durable, Sonata watches can fit every budget and wardrobe with ease. Their range perfectly combines fashion and function. You can also check out the Sonata Stride smartwatches to get the best of both worlds.<\\/p><h3>\\u2022 TraQ<\\/h3><p>TraQ smartwatches range by Titan is a highly sophisticated fitness watch that helps you track your activities. Durable and stylish, <b><a style=\\\"color: #1a75ff;\\\" title=\\\"TraQ watches\\\" href=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.titan.co.in\\/shop\\/traq-by-titan\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\" rel=\\\"noopener\\\"> TraQ watches<\\/a><\\/b> are the real deal both for men and women. From measuring your steps to calories, distance and more, you can have it all with TraQ.<\\/p><h3>\\u2022 Xylys<\\/h3><p>An exclusive brand of <b><a style=\\\"color: #1a75ff;\\\" href=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.titan.co.in\\/shop\\/xylys\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\" rel=\\\"noopener\\\">Swiss watches<\\/a><\\/b> by Titan, Xylys represents uniqueness in designs with its range of aesthetically pleasing timepieces. Reasonably p