riced with over 100 ergonomically designed models, you can take your pick online.<\\/p><h3>\\u2022 Nebula<\\/h3><p>The exclusive and luxurious watch collection from Titan \\u2013 Nebula comprises a variety of <b><a style=\\\"color: #1a75ff;\\\" href=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.titan.co.in\\/shop\\/nebula\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\" rel=\\\"noopener\\\">18k solid gold jewellery watches<\\/a><\\/b>. With over 100 thoughtfully blended watch designs, Nebula brings together the rich Indian heritage and fine watchmaking craftsmanship.<\\/p><h3>\\u2022 Zoop<\\/h3><p>Choose from a wide variety of kids watches that are fun, durable and bold. From superhero-themed watches for boys to Disney princess watches for girls, surprise your kids with cool new watches!<\\/p><h2>International Brands<\\/h2><h3>\\u2022 Kenneth Cole<\\/h3><p>The famous American watch brand, Kenneth Cole, offers fashionable and casual quality timepieces. From the classic silver dial to colourful variants, you can choose from a range of watches online at Titan\'s official website.<\\/p><h3>\\u2022 Tommy Hilfiger<\\/h3><p>Who isn\'t familiar with Tommy Hilfiger? With a watch range that goes from simple to designer, Tommy Hilfiger watches are a class apart and popular since they began. You can find a plethora of options online, both for men and women. When it\'s Tommy Hilfiger, you do not have to worry about quality and style.<\\/p><h3>\\u2022 Lee Cooper<\\/h3><p>Lee Cooper watches\' collection can be described as suave and chic. With stylish designs and durable quality, Lee Cooper offers wristwatches that are worth every penny of yours. Opt for these watches for an impactful casual look. Choose from the latest range available online at Titan Watches.<\\/p><h3>\\u2022 Anne Klein<\\/h3><p>A popular brand in women\'s fashion, Anne Klein is known for its elegant and feminine watch designs. This brand aims to depict how women live and creates timepieces that match their lifestyle and choices.<\\/p><h3>\\u2022 Coach<\\/h3><p