(394, 88, '_elementor_data', '[{\"id\":\"67aa675\",\"elType\":\"section\",\"settings\":[],\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"340e4d4\",\"elType\":\"column\",\"settings\":{\"_column_size\":100,\"_inline_size\":null},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"094be5a\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"editor\":\"\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"text-editor\"}],\"isInner\":false}],\"isInner\":false},{\"id\":\"15d299f\",\"elType\":\"section\",\"settings\":{\"layout\":\"full_width\"},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"f297fce\",\"elType\":\"column\",\"settings\":{\"_column_size\":100,\"_inline_size\":null},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"9426408\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"image\":{\"url\":\"http:\\/\\/localhost\\/wordpress2\\/wordpress\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2023\\/03\\/titan15.png\",\"id\":58,\"size\":\"\",\"alt\":\"\",\"source\":\"library\"}},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"image\"}],\"isInner\":false}],\"isInner\":false},{\"id\":\"75b8590\",\"elType\":\"section\",\"settings\":[],\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"b2e5bcb\",\"elType\":\"column\",\"settings\":{\"_column_size\":100,\"_inline_size\":null},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"2bcfa6a\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"editor\":\"<h1>Titan Watches<\\/h1><p>For people seeking effortless class, sophistication, and luxury, a stylish watch is worth the investment. A timeless watch project prestige, confidence, and class. So, if you\'re planning to add a new watch to your collection, you must shop for top branded watches from a reputable watch shop. At Titan, we offer a wide collection of authentic <b><a style=\\\"color: #1a75ff;\\\" title=\\\"branded watches\\\" href=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.titan.co.in\\/our-brands\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\" rel=\\\"noopener\\\"> branded watches<\\/a><\\/b> all under one roof. You can filter your choices for a better experience according to price, discounts, gender, brand, function, and more. We always strive to provide our customers with the best service possible when it comes to shopping for tasteful watches.<\\/p><h2>Buy Watches Online<\\/h2><p>A watch is an accessory that showcases your personality once you find the perfect match. Whether you\'re after a classic and timeless design or something that is edgy and funky, Titan Watches has it all. With the expansion of the online market, you can now avail thousands of product options in just a few clicks. From classic vintage models to the latest high-functioning <b><a style=\\\"color: #1a75ff;\\\" title=\\\"smartwatches online\\\" href=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.titan.co.in\\/shop\\/smart\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\" rel=\\\"noopener\\\"> smartwatches<\\/a><\\/b>, you can have the world on your wrist.<br \\/>Buying watches online can give you a lot of benefits, including endless options, value for money, the convenience of time, offers, and <b><a style=\\\"color: #1a75ff;\\\" title=\\\"discounts on Watches\\\" href=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.titan.co.in\\/shop\\/offers\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\" rel=\\\"noopener\\\">discounts<\\/a><\\/b>. So, choose from a myriad of options and get ready to receive compliments wherever you go.<\\/p><h2>Get the Best Watch Price Online<\\/h2><p>At Titan, we ensure that there is transparency in pricing while you shop for watches online. With great deals and offers available on our online store, you can be sure of affordable pricing according to your budget. You can even filter the products in the bracket of your suitable price range to get the best deal. Shopping for watches from an online store gives you the freedom to choose without any time constraint.<\\/p><h3>\\u2022 Variety of watches available<\\/h3><p>You can view and browse through thousands of watches online, which almost impossible to do physically.<\\/p><h3>\\u2022 You can save money<\\/h3><p>Online shopping is a great way to save on your precious money. You can avail of great deals and offers on watches online, which is not always applicable in store.<\\/p><h3>\\u2022 Easy exchange\\/return policies<\\/h3><p>Online shopping has made the <b><a style=\\\"color: #1a75ff;\\\" title=\\\"Exchange &amp; return Policy\\\" href=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.titan.co.in\\/faq?category=Returns%20and%20exchanges\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\" rel=\\\"noopener\\\"> process of exchange <\\/a><\\/b> and returns easier than ever. You just need to send an exchange\\/return request online on the retailer\'s website, and your order will be collected from your address. However, before doing so, make sure to get through the policy guidelines for better understanding.<\\/p><h3>\\u2022 Doorstep service available<\\/h3><p>Unlike regular shopping, online shopping gets your stuff delivered to your doorstep. No matter the product, you just have to place an order from your smartphone or laptop.<\\/p><h2>Top Branded Watches for Men and Women<\\/h2><p>Today, the fashion world has evolved, and there is no just \'for men\' or \'for women.\' Unisex trends are topping the charts, be it clothing or <b><a style=\\\"color: #1a75ff;\\\" title=\\\"accessories online\\\" href=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.titan.co.in\\/shop\\/titan\\/product-category=belts+straps+wallets\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\" rel=\\\"noopener\\\"> accessories<\\/a><\\/b>. Men and women are both breaking the usual fashion norms and experimenting with all kinds of accessories. And watches are no exception. If you too want to step out of your comfort zone, you can now go for ultra-stylish branded watches from Titan. From <b><a style=\\\"color: #1a75ff;\\\" title=\\\"Tommy Hilfiger Watches Online\\\" href=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.titan.co.in\\/shop\\/tommy-hilfiger\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\" rel=\\\"noopener\\\">Tommy Hilfiger<\\/a><\\/b> to <b><a style=\\\"color: #1a75ff;\\\" title=\\\"Olivia Burton Watches Online\\\" href=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.titan.co.in\\/shop\\/olivia-burton\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\" rel=\\\"noopener\\\">Olivia Burton<\\/a><\\/b>, you can choose from a variety of top international brands online. <br \\/>Here are some of the top brands available at Titan watches:<\\/p><h3>\\u2022 Fastrack<\\/h3><p>Fastrack is the brand of the youth. One of Titan\'s own products, <b><a style=\\\"color: #1a75ff;\\\" title=\\\"Fastrack watches\\\" href=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.titan.co.in\\/shop\\/watches\\/brand=fastrack\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\" rel=\\\"noopener\\\">Fastrack watches<\\/a><\\/b>, aims to complement millennial\'s active lifestyle and trends. From smartwatches to <b><a style=\\\"color: #1a75ff;\\\" title=\\\"analog watches\\\" href=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.titan.co.in\\/shop\\/analog-watches\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\" rel=\\\"noopener\\\"> analog watches<\\/a><\\/b>, you can find a variety of styles and designs online on our website.<\\/p><h3>\\u2022 Sonata<\\/h3><p>A bold and contemporary product of TATA, to <b><a style=\\\"color: #1a75ff;\\\" title=\\\"Sonata watches\\\" href=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.titan.co.in\\/shop\\/sonata-watches\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\" rel=\\\"noopener\\\"> Sonata watches<\\/a><\\/b> accentuate every outfit with their classic designs. Affordable and durable, Sonata watches can fit every budget and wardrobe with ease. Their range perfectly combines fashion and function. You can also check out the Sonata Stride smartwatches to get the best of both worlds.<\\/p><h3>\\u2022 TraQ<\\/h3><p>TraQ smartwatches range by Titan is a highly sophisticated fitness watch that helps you track your activities. Durable and stylish, <b><a style=\\\"color: #1a75ff;\\\" title=\\\"TraQ watches\\\" href=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.titan.co.in\\/shop\\/traq-by-titan\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\" rel=\\\"noopener\\\"> TraQ watches<\\/a><\\/b> are the real deal both for men and women. From measuring your steps to calories, distance and more, you can have it all with TraQ.<\\/p><h3>\\u2022 Xylys<\\/h3><p>An exclusive brand of <b><a style=\\\"color: #1a75ff;\\\" href=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.titan.co.in\\/shop\\/xylys\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\" rel=\\\"noopener\\\">Swiss watches<\\/a><\\/b> by Titan, Xylys represents uniqueness in designs with its range of aesthetically pleasing timepieces. Reasonably priced with over 100 ergonomically designed models, you can take your pick online.<\\/p><h3>\\u2022 Nebula<\\/h3><p>The exclusive and luxurious watch collection from Titan \\u2013 Nebula comprises a variety of <b><a style=\\\"color: #1a75ff;\\\" href=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.titan.co.in\\/shop\\/nebula\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\" rel=\\\"noopener\\\">18k solid gold jewellery watches<\\/a><\\/b>. With over 100 thoughtfully blended watch designs, Nebula brings together the rich Indian heritage and fine watchmaking craftsmanship.<\\/p><h3>\\u2022 Zoop<\\/h3><p>Choose from a wide variety of kids watches that are fun, durable and bold. From superhero-themed watches for boys to Disney princess watches for girls, surprise your kids with cool new watches!<\\/p><h2>International Brands<\\/h2><h3>\\u2022 Kenneth Cole<\\/h3><p>The famous American watch brand, Kenneth Cole, offers fashionable and casual quality timepieces. From the classic silver dial to colourful variants, you can choose from a range of watches online at Titan\'s official website.<\\/p><h3>\\u2022 Tommy Hilfiger<\\/h3><p>Who isn\'t familiar with Tommy Hilfiger? With a watch range that goes from simple to designer, Tommy Hilfiger watches are a class apart and popular since they began. You can find a plethora of options online, both for men and women. When it\'s Tommy Hilfiger, you do not have to worry about quality and style.<\\/p><h3>\\u2022 Lee Cooper<\\/h3><p>Lee Cooper watches\' collection can be described as suave and chic. With stylish designs and durable quality, Lee Cooper offers wristwatches that are worth every penny of yours. Opt for these watches for an impactful casual look. Choose from the latest range available online at Titan Watches.<\\/p><h3>\\u2022 Anne Klein<\\/h3><p>A popular brand in women\'s fashion, Anne Klein is known for its elegant and feminine watch designs. This brand aims to depict how women live and creates timepieces that match their lifestyle and choices.<\\/p><h3>\\u2022 Coach<\\/h3><p>Coach watches are authentic in design, elegant and beautiful. Their watches are Swiss made by Movado. Available in a host of designs and colours, visit our website for more information.<\\/p><h3>\\u2022 Police<\\/h3><p>Launched in 2003, Police watches appeals to the masses and offers haute couture timepieces. From casual street style to formal workwear watches, you can get it all. Pick your best fit from our official website and avail of great deals and offers.<\\/p><p>\\u00a0<\\/p>\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"text-editor\"}],\"isInner\":false}],\"isInner\":false},{\"id\":\"5c0d0f8\",\"elType\":\"section\",\"settings\":{\"structure\":\"21\"},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"0c070d0\",\"elType\":\"column\",\"settings\":{\"_column_size\":33,\"_inline_size\":null},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"32add66\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"editor\":\"<div class=\\\"flex flex-grow flex-col gap-3\\\"><div class=\\\"min-h-[20px] flex flex-col items-start gap-4 whitespace-pre-wrap\\\"><div class=\\\"markdown prose w-full break-words dark:prose-invert light\\\"><p>Square watches are a timeless classic that have been popular for decades. They offer a unique and stylish look that sets them apart from traditional round watches. Square watches are perfect for those who want to make a bold fashion statement or add a touch of sophistication to their wardrobe.<\\/p><p>One of the main advantages of square watches is their versatility. They can be dressed up or down, making them suitable for a wide range of occasions. Whether you are looking for a watch to wear to work, a formal event, or a casual outing with friends, a square watch is the perfect accessory to complement your style.<\\/p><p>Another great thing about square watches is that they come in a variety of designs, colors, and materials. From sleek and modern stainless steel to classic leather straps, you can find a square watch that fits your personal style and preferences. Some popular brands that offer square watches include Rolex, Cartier, and TAG Heuer.<\\/p><p>If you are looking for a watch that is both stylish and practical, a square watch is a great choice. They offer excellent functionality and durability, making them perfect for everyday wear. Plus, their unique design ensures that they stand out from the crowd, making them a conversation starter wherever you go.<\\/p><p>In conclusion, square watches are a timeless and stylish accessory that every watch enthusiast should consider adding to their collection. Whether you are looking for a classic design or something more modern, there is a square watch out there for you.<\\/p><\\/div><p>\\u00a0<\\/p><\\/div><\\/div>\",\"text_color\":\"#7A7A7AF5\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"text-editor\"}],\"isInner\":false},{\"id\":\"3db6ce4\",\"elType\":\"column\",\"settings\":{\"_column_size\":66,\"_inline_size\":null},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"e97a461\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"image\":{\"url\":\"http:\\/\\/localhost\\/wordpress2\\/wordpress\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2023\\/03\\/titan20.jpg\",\"id\":62,\"size\":\"\",\"source\":\"library\",\"alt\":\"\"},\"image_size\":\"2048x2048\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"image\"}],\"isInner\":false}],\"isInner\":false},{\"id\":\"24a4607\",\"elType\":\"section\",\"settings\":[],\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"59f633c\",\"elType\":\"column\",\"settings\":{\"_column_size\":100,\"_inline_size\":null},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"4dac794\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"smartsliderid\":\"2\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"smartslider\"}],\"isInner\":false}],\"isInner\":false}]'),
