(654, 127, '_elementor_data', '[{\"id\":\"da84838\",\"elType\":\"section\",\"settings\":[],\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"c695fa8\",\"elType\":\"column\",\"settings\":{\"_column_size\":100,\"_inline_size\":null},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"0d42113\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"image\":{\"url\":\"http:\\/\\/localhost\\/wordpress2\\/wordpress\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2023\\/03\\/titan6.jpg\",\"id\":32,\"size\":\"\",\"alt\":\"\",\"source\":\"library\"}},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"image\"},{\"id\":\"8ae334c\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"editor\":\"<h1 class=\\\"hero__title\\\">\\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0About Us<\\/h1><div class=\\\"hero__description\\\">\\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 The Titan Company Limited (Titan) Journey began<\\/div><div class=\\\"hero__description\\\">\\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 with small but confident steps in 1984 as a joint a<\\/div><div class=\\\"hero__description\\\">\\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0between the TATA Group and Tamil Nadu Industrial<\\/div><div class=\\\"hero__description\\\">\\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0Development Corporation (TIDCO). Started with an<\\/div><div class=\\\"hero__description\\\">\\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0objective to create a Titan watch for everyone has<\\/div><div class=\\\"hero__description\\\">\\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0now grown to be the fifth largest integrated watch<\\/div><div class=\\\"hero__description\\\">\\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 manufacturer in the world which was only\\u00a0<\\/div><div class=\\\"hero__description\\\">\\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 the beginning of a success story.<\\/div>\",\"_margin\":{\"unit\":\"px\",\"top\":\"-336\",\"right\":\"0\",\"bottom\":\"0\",\"left\":\"0\",\"isLinked\":false}},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"text-editor\"}],\"isInner\":false}],\"isInner\":false},{\"id\":\"8525691\",\"elType\":\"section\",\"settings\":{\"structure\":\"31\"},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"7a7e2d3\",\"elType\":\"column\",\"settings\":{\"_column_size\":25,\"_inline_size\":null},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"48ca83c\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"editor\":\"<p>\\u00a0<\\/p><div class=\\\"heritage__title scroll-fade in-view\\\" style=\\\"font-family: \'Playfair Display\', serif; transition: all 0.8s ease 0.2s; opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0px); will-change: transform; font-size: 3.6rem; color: #00b2ad; line-height: 1.5em; background-color: #ffffff;\\\">Overview<\\/div><div class=\\\"heritage__content scroll-fade in-view\\\" style=\\\"transition: all 0.8s ease 0.2s; opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0px); will-change: transform; color: #000000; font-family: Raleway, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; background-color: #ffffff;\\\"><p style=\\\"margin: 15px;\\\">Titan Company Limited (Titan), a joint venture between the Tata Group and the Tamil Nadu Industrial Development Corporation (TIDCO), commenced its operations in 1984 under the name Titan Watches Limited. Titan is the fifth largest integrated own brand watch manufacturer in the world. Over the last three decades, Titan has expanded into underpenetrated markets and created lifestyle brands across different product categories. Titan is widely known for transforming the watch and jewellery industry in India and for shaping India\'s retail market by pioneering experiential retail.<\\/p><\\/div>\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"text-editor\"}],\"isInner\":false},{\"id\":\"740ae4c\",\"elType\":\"column\",\"settings\":{\"_column_size\":25,\"_inline_size\":null},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"9400e94\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"editor\":\"<div>\\u00a0<\\/div><div>\\u00a0<\\/div><div class=\\\"heritage__title scroll-fade in-view\\\" style=\\\"font-family: \'Playfair Display\', serif; transition: all 0.8s ease 0.2s; opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0px); will-change: transform; font-size: 3.6rem; color: #00b2ad; line-height: 1.5em; background-color: #ffffff;\\\">Philosophy<\\/div><div class=\\\"heritage__content scroll-fade in-view\\\" style=\\\"transition: all 0.8s ease 0.2s; opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0px); will-change: transform; color: #000000; font-family: Raleway, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; background-color: #ffffff;\\\"><p style=\\\"margin: 15px;\\\">The name Titan today evokes superior craftsmanship, innovative technology and trustworthy product quality.<\\/p><div class=\\\"heritage__content scroll-fade in-view\\\" style=\\\"transition: all 0.8s ease 0.2s; opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0px); will-change: transform;\\\"><p style=\\\"margin: 15px;\\\">\\u00a0<\\/p><\\/div><\\/div>\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"text-editor\"}],\"isInner\":false},{\"id\":\"b9de152\",\"elType\":\"column\",\"settings\":{\"_column_size\":50,\"_inline_size\":null},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"d64016f\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"image\":{\"url\":\"http:\\/\\/localhost\\/wordpress2\\/wordpress\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2023\\/03\\/titan8.png\",\"id\":40,\"size\":\"\",\"alt\":\"\",\"source\":\"library\"}},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"image\"}],\"isInner\":false}],\"isInner\":false},{\"id\":\"b497f7f\",\"elType\":\"section\",\"settings\":{\"structure\":\"22\"},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"d7a86c0\",\"elType\":\"column\",\"settings\":{\"_column_size\":66,\"_inline_size\":null},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"b8619b4\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"editor\":\"<p>\\u00a0<\\/p><div class=\\\"heritage__title scroll-fade in-view\\\" style=\\\"font-family: \'Playfair Display\', serif; transition: all 0.8s ease 0.2s; opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0px); will-change: transform; font-size: 3.6rem; color: #00b2ad; line-height: 1.5em; background-color: #ffffff;\\\">Our Values<\\/div><div class=\\\"heritage__content scroll-fade in-view\\\" style=\\\"transition: all 0.8s ease 0.2s; opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0px); will-change: transform; color: #000000; font-family: Raleway, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; background-color: #ffffff;\\\"><p style=\\\"margin: 15px 15px 35px;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-weight: bold;\\\">Customer first:<\\/span>\\u00a0Customers take precedence over all else, always.<\\/p><p style=\\\"margin: 15px 15px 35px;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-weight: bold;\\\">People make the brand:<\\/span>\\u00a0Titanians are at the heart of our success and that is why their dreams and aspirations are at the forefront of our brand policy.<\\/p><p style=\\\"margin: 15px 15px 35px;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-weight: bold;\\\">Culture and teamwork:<\\/span>\\u00a0High performance is a way of life.<\\/p><p style=\\\"margin: 15px 15px 35px;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-weight: bold;\\\">Creativity and innovation:<\\/span>\\u00a0Driven by innovation and creativity, we focus on smarter approaches and newer technologies.<\\/p><p style=\\\"margin: 15px 15px 35px;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-weight: bold;\\\">Passion for excellence:\\u00a0<\\/span>In all our pursuits, we ceaselessly strive for excellence.<\\/p><p style=\\\"margin: 15px;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-weight: bold;\\\">Corporate citizenship:<\\/span>\\u00a0We ensure that a part of our resources is invested in environment and community betterment.<\\/p><\\/div>\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"text-editor\"}],\"isInner\":false},{\"id\":\"eb99617\",\"elType\":\"column\",\"settings\":{\"_column_size\":33,\"_inline_size\":null},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"a781971\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"editor\":\"<p>\\u00a0<\\/p><p><span style=\\\"color: #00b2ad; font-family: \'Playfair Display\', serif; font-size: 36px; font-style: italic; font-weight: bold; background-color: #ffffff;\\\">\\\"Titan Company Limited continues to grow and set new standards for innovation and quality with each new offering.\\\"<\\/span><\\/p>\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"text-editor\"}],\"isInner\":false}],\"isInner\":false},{\"id\":\"0794a4e\",\"elType\":\"section\",\"settings\":{\"structure\":\"20\"},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"9f831a3\",\"elType\":\"column\",\"settings\":{\"_column_size\":50,\"_inline_size\":null},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"5cd3004\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"image\":{\"url\":\"http:\\/\\/localhost\\/wordpress2\\/wordpress\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2023\\/03\\/titan10.png\",\"id\":42,\"size\":\"\",\"alt\":\"\",\"source\":\"library\"}},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"image\"}],\"isInner\":false},{\"id\":\"6699d2f\",\"elType\":\"column\",\"settings\":{\"_column_size\":50,\"_inline_size\":null},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"02f3fb4\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"editor\":\"<div class=\\\"heritage__title scroll-fade in-view\\\" style=\\\"font-family: \'Playfair Display\', serif; transition: all 0.8s ease 0.2s; opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0px); will-change: transform; font-size: 3.6rem; color: #00b2ad; line-height: 1.5em; background-color: #ffffff;\\\">Our Promise<\\/div><div class=\\\"heritage__content scroll-fade in-view\\\" style=\\\"transition: all 0.8s ease 0.2s; opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0px); will-change: transform; color: #000000; font-family: Raleway, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; background-color: #ffffff;\\\"><p style=\\\"margin: 15px 15px 35px;\\\">Pioneering innovation, international design ethos, customer-oriented values and top-notch service have always formed the cornerstones for brand Titan.<\\/p><p>\\u00a0<\\/p><p style=\\\"margin: 15px 15px 35px;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-weight: bold;\\\">International styling<\\/span><br \\/>Titan strives to promote styles that are at par with the international standards. We bring together high quality materials and innovative technologies to give you products that are unique and exceptional.<\\/p><p>\\u00a0<\\/p><p style=\\\"margin: 15px 15px 35px;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-weight: bold;\\\">Unparalleled post sale services<\\/span><br \\/>A testimony to this notion stands in the fact that Nebula watches come with a lifetime warranty while Titan Eyeplus offers free insurance for prescriptions spectacles. This only speaks volumes about the commitment towards the customers to provide the best services and experience.<\\/p><p>\\u00a0<\\/p><p>\\u00a0<\\/p><p style=\\\"margin: 15px;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-weight: bold;\\\">Mark of quality<\\/span><br \\/>Passion for the highest standards in jewellery making and design provided an impetus for Tanishq, one of India\\u2019s most trusted brands, to introduce innovations like Karatmeter which helpes consumers check the purity of gold and discern the quality of the jewellery.<\\/p><\\/div>\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"text-editor\"}],\"isInner\":false}],\"isInner\":false}]'),
